90001125.desc:
2 FIRE Monster + 1 "BurnTRAP" Trap Card
You can use each of the following effects of "BurnTRAP White Knight" only once per turn. You can either send 1 Trap Card you control or a Trap Card from your hand to the Graveyard; inflict damage to your opponent equal to this card's ATK. If you inflicted effect damage to your opponent this turn: You can Set 1 "BurnTRAP" Trap Card from your Deck.

{/}

90001126.desc:
1 "BurnTRAP" Monster + 1 "BurnTRAP" Trap Card
If this card is Trick Summoned: You can destroy 1 monster on the field. Your opponent cannot activate cards or effects in response to this effect's activation. Each Time a Trap card is activated, Inflict 500 Damage to your opponent immediately after it resolves.

{/}

90001127.desc:
1 FIRE Monster + 1+ Trap Card
The Base ATK & DEF of this card is the number of Trap Card used to Trick Summon this card x 1000.  You can use each of the following effects of "BurnTRAP Cavalry" only once per turn. You can inflict damage to your opponent equal to this card's ATK, also you cannot conduct your Battle Phase this Turn. If this card is destroyed by battle or card effect: You can target Trap Cards in your GY up to the number of Trap Cards used to Trick Summon this card; Set them to your side of the field.

{/}

90001131.desc:
1 FIRE Monster + 2 Trap Cards
You can use each of the following effects of "BurnTRAP Galaxy Coder" only once per turn. If this card is Trick Summoned: You can reveal 3 "BurnTRAP" Trap Cards from your Deck; add 2 random cards from among those cards to your Hand, also your cannot Special Summon monsters for the rest of this turn, except "BurnTRAP" Monsters. Once per turn: You can shuffle up to 3 Trap cards from your GY into the Deck; Destroy cards up to the number of Trap cards shuffled back by this effect.

{/}

90001132.desc:
2 Trick Monster + 4 Trap Cards
Must be Trick Summoned and cannot be Special Summon by other ways. Cannot be used as material for a Trick Summon. Cannot be targeted or destroyed by your opponent's card effects. Once per turn, when a card or effect is activated (Quick Effect): You can discard 1 card; negate the activation, then you can set 1 Trap Card from your Hand or GY.

{/}

99910100.desc:
Activate 1 of these effects;
●If "Sea of Trees" is on the field: Special Summon 1 "YuYuYu" Pendulum Monster face-up from your Extra Deck.
●If "Sea of Trees" is not on the field: Activate 1 "Sea of Trees" from your Deck, and if you do, add 1 "YuYuYu" Fairy monster from your Deck or GY to your hand.

76175568.desc:
1 Fairy monster + Counter Trap
If this card is Trick Summoned: You can move this card to another Main Monster Zone. This Effect cannot be negated. Once per turn, while "The Sanctuary in the Sky" is face-up on the field: You can send 1 Fairy monster from your Deck to the GY; add 1 Counter Trap from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each of the following effects of "Fairy of the Forest" once per turn. During your Main Phase: You can discard 1 card; either add to your hand or Special Summon 1 Level 4 LIGHT Fairy monster from your Deck or GY. If this card is destroyed: You can target 1 Counter Trap in your GY; Set it.


{/}

30000085.desc:
Activate 1 of these effects;
● Select 1 monster in your hand and show it to your opponent, then roll a six-sided die. If the result is 1, send the selected monster to the Graveyard. If the result is 2-6, the Level of the selected monster becomes equal to the result until the end of this turn.
● If you control "Kozaky": Reveal 1 monster in your hand, then declare a Level from 1 to 6; it becomes that Level until the end of this turn.

