34259423.desc:
2 "Helios" Monster + 1 "Macro Cosmos"
Must First be Trick Summoned. This card cannot be used as a Trick Material Monster. While this card is face-up on the field, any card sent to the GY is banished instead. This card's ATK/DEF become the number of banished cards x 400. You can use the following effects of "Helios - the Primordial God" only once per turn. During the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can Special Summon 1 "Helios" monster from your Hand or Deck. During the End Phase, if this card was banished while face-up on the field, this turn: Special Summon this banished card.

